<div class="form_signup_flame">
  <span class="form_box_h1">创建账户</span>
  <div class="form_box_signup">
    <span class="form_box_h2">小伙伴们快来注册吧!</span>
    <span class="form_back">或者  <%= link_to '登录', signin_path ,class: "form_back_font"%></span>
    <%= render 'form' %>
  </div>
  <div class="signup_other">
    <div class="other_box1">
      <%= image_tag 'foot.png', class: "other_icon"%>
      <div class="other_box_word">
        <span class="other_box_h">计划和记录</span>
        <span class="other_box_p">抛开空想和等待，让学习和实践充实生活；在这里留下你走向成功的每一个脚印。</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="other_box2">
      <%= image_tag 'friends.png', class: "other_icon"%>
      <div class="other_box_word">
        <span class="other_box_h">收获与分享</span>
        <span class="other_box_p">和朋友们互相分享脚踏实地的历程；走过太多的生活百态，一路总有你陪伴。</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="other_box3">
      <%= image_tag 'fork.png', class: "other_icon"%>
      <div class="other_box_word">
        <span class="other_box_h">自媒体平台</span>
        <span class="other_box_p">建立你的微项目供其他小伙伴们收藏&拷贝；说自己想说的话，打造属于你自己的的媒体。</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <span class="other_box4">米er,让你的生活更加丰富多彩,无论用手机、平板还是电脑。</span>
  </div>
</div>
